@startuml
title abtop-py Component Architecture

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

actor "User" as User

component "CLI\nargparse" as CLI
component "MultiCollector" as MultiCollector
component "ClaudeCollector" as ClaudeCollector
component "CodexCollector" as CodexCollector
component "Process, Port,\nand Git Helpers" as Helpers
component "Rate Limit\nReaders and Cache" as RateLimits
component "CursesUI" as TUI
component "Text and JSON\nOutput" as Output

database "Local Files\nsessions, transcripts,\nconfig, cache" as Files
cloud "Operating System\n/proc, ps, lsof, git" as OS

User --> CLI : runs command
CLI --> MultiCollector : creates collector
CLI --> TUI : interactive mode
CLI --> Output : --once / --json
TUI --> MultiCollector : refresh loop
Output --> MultiCollector : collect once

MultiCollector --> ClaudeCollector : collect Claude sessions
MultiCollector --> CodexCollector : collect Codex sessions
MultiCollector --> Helpers : process tree, ports, git stats
MultiCollector --> RateLimits : quota data

ClaudeCollector --> Files : .claude sessions and JSONL
CodexCollector --> Files : .codex rollout JSONL
RateLimits --> Files : abtop rate-limit cache
Helpers --> OS : local process and filesystem state

MultiCollector --> TUI : AgentSession list
MultiCollector --> Output : snapshot data
@enduml
